    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's all gone. the last ten years... all those papers, the grants, the theory... it was all based on a fundamental error i missed. i feel like a complete fraud. there is literally nothing left of me now that the work is dead. i dont even know why i'm still waking up.",
