    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild? i dont want to rebuild. there is nothing left to build with. it's not just that i'm lost, it's that the person who was doing the work... that person doesn't even exist. the \"me\" people knew was a lie. i've just been playing a part for a decade and now the curtain has dropped. it feels like the most honest thing to do is just to stop. to just stop everything.",
